==English==
===Verb===
used as an expression of strong preference or approbation; = "what I would have is ---", "I am for ---", "commend me to ---", etc.

:''Give me'' the good old times!--Edward Lytton (1873)

:''Give me'' the pliant minde, whose gentle measure Complies and suits with all estates.--George Herbert, ''Temple, Church, Content,'' (1633) iv

